<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There are hereby authorized to be appropriated such sums,<ref class="footnoteRef" idref="fn002030">1</ref><note type="footnote" id="fn002030"><num>1</num> So in original. The comma probably should not appear.</note> as may be necessary to carry out the provisions and purposes of this chapter.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id60069c0d-3a70-11f1-83b4-f01f82055b58">(<ref href="/us/act/1954-08-31/ch1156/s8">Aug. 31, 1954, ch. 1156, § 8</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/68/1011">68 Stat. 1011</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/102/486/tXXV/s2504/d/3">Pub. L. 102–486, title XXV, § 2504(d)(3)</ref>, <date date="1992-10-24">Oct. 24, 1992</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/106/3106">106 Stat. 3106</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
