<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="id60069c10-3a70-11f1-83b4-f01f82055b58"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">1992—<ref href="/us/pl/102/486">Pub. L. 102–486</ref> struck out “not to exceed $500,000 annually,” after “such sums,”.</p>
